hicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Par <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/mmrdesign"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3f4b28db256cb702efd3a27f0aa8572c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3f4b28db256cb702efd3a27f0aa8572c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/mmrdesign" class="reviewer-name">mmrdesign</a> le <span class="review-date">décembre 17, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">I use this plugin for 3 websites. 1 is paid version. Its work good. And support is very good</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">Great plugin for translating websites</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="5 sur 5 étoiles" data-title-template="%s sur 5 étoiles" data-rating="5" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Par <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/scepterus"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cabd8861b5dd9187d24004dbfba70038?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cabd8861b5dd9187d24004dbfba70038?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/scepterus" class="reviewer-name">scepterus</a> le <span class="review-date">décembre 17, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">I was recently tasked with building a bilingual website which I have not done before.\nat first, I thought I needed duplicate pages for each page, one for each language, but then I found this plugin.\n\nin short, it allows you to have the same website in as many languages as you can possibly wish, and that includes different images, links and menus among other things.\n\nhighly recommended for localizing websites and other uses that this can be applied to.</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">Create translations the simple way</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="5 sur 5 étoiles" data-title-template="%s sur 5 étoiles" data-rating="5" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Par <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/marcomedia"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b87d2fee6038f60dbe18693e49cecc7c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b87d2fee6038f60dbe18693e49cecc7c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/marcomedia" class="reviewer-name"> <small>(marcoMedia)</small></a> le <span class="review-date">décembre 15, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">I have tried a lot of translate plugins but this one does it all. Some plugins are too big to handle (you know what I am talking about) some are too small and can\'t do this or can\'t do that. This one does it all. Ok, if you want more you pay for it. Take it from me, it is worth all your money. Try the free version and if you need more then two languages buy the personal version. It makes live easier and will loose you less hours work.</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">after 1.8.9 update site crashed!!</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="5 sur 5 étoiles" data-title-template="%s sur 5 étoiles" data-rating="5" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Par <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/0x0a0f"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3591eedce193cb03bf5da643b919ba53?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3591eedce193cb03bf5da643b919ba53?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/0x0a0f" class="reviewer-name">0x0a0f</a> le <span class="review-date">décembre 16, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">today while hitting update button for this plugin site and server crashed with continuous traffic to and from google (inspected system). when removing plugin folder traffic stops but web site is down... have to recover from a backup.\n\nUpdate. 5 stars from me for the developer support. Bugs hap