bd062c8132809641c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/mrmatteastwood" class="reviewer-name">MrMattEastwood</a> le <span class="review-date">août 25, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">This plugin offers premium features at the low price of free: the post import function works well and I like how flexible and useful the shortcode is. I also think the back-end UI is intuitive, and I got a friendly and competent response when I posted in the support forum.</div>\n</div>\n";}s:17:"short_description";s:142:"The most powerful WordPress RSS aggregator, helping you curate content, autoblog, import and display unlimited RSS feeds within a few minutes.";s:13:"download_link";s:59:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/feedzy-rss-feeds.zip";s:11:"screenshots";a:6:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:"src";s:69:"https://ps.w.org/feedzy-rss-feeds/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1569422";s:7:"caption";s:14:"Simple example";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:"src";s:69:"https://ps.w.org/feedzy-rss-feeds/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1569422";s:7:"caption";s:36:"Inserting a shortcode in the WYSIWYG";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:"src";s:69:"https://ps.w.org/feedzy-rss-feeds/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=1569422";s:7:"caption";s:12:"Widget admin";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:"src";s:69:"https://ps.w.org/feedzy-rss-feeds/assets/screenshot-4.jpg?rev=1569422";s:7:"caption";s:13:"Widget render";}i:5;a:2:{s:3:"src";s:69:"https://ps.w.org/feedzy-rss-feeds/assets/screenshot-5.jpg?rev=1659405";s:7:"caption";b:0;}i:6;a:2:{s:3:"src";s:69:"https://ps.w.org/feedzy-rss-feeds/assets/screenshot-6.jpg?rev=1659405";s:7:"caption";b:0;}}s:8:"versions";a:97:{s:3:"1.0";s:63:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/feedzy-rss-feeds.1.0.zip";s:4:"1.01";s:64:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/feedzy-rss-feeds.1.01.zip";s:4:"1.02";s:64:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/feedzy-rss-feeds.1.02.zip";s:4:"1.03";s:64:"https://downloads