>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">Hello,\nI need to do a fresh install of this plugin.\nWhen I deleted the plugin I want to make sure everything is gone before reinstall.\nCan you confirm with me that the folder called slider2 with about 6 jpegs called freelayerslider under wp-content/uploads belongs to this plugin.\n\nAlso would like to know if the folder themeisle-gutenberg also belongs to this plugin?\n\nThank you. Let me know.</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">Useful Plugin</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="5 sur 5 étoiles" data-title-template="%s sur 5 étoiles" data-rating="5" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Par <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/mahrus21"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/334d3d9b508eaba4edfa5f2e803e09a1?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/334d3d9b508eaba4edfa5f2e803e09a1?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/mahrus21" class="reviewer-name">mahrus21</a> le <span class="review-date">novembre 11, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">Thank you so much</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">Buen complemento</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="5 sur 5 étoiles" da