oved sync library from POST to GET method</li>\n<li>Fix: <code>ucwords</code> support for older php versions (<a href="https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/7327" rel="nofollow ugc">#7327</a>, <a href="https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/7310" rel="nofollow ugc">#7310</a>)</li>\n<li>Fix: Background self hosted videos responsive</li>\n<li>Fix: Group controls <code>conditions</code> support</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.5.2 &#8211; 2019-03-05</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Custom space between widgets override (<a href="https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/7309" rel="nofollow ugc">#7309</a>)</li>\n<li>Fix: Changed the default width of Absolute &amp; Fixed position widget (<a href="https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/7311" rel="nofollow ugc">#7311</a>)</li>\n<li><strong>Note: This fix might affect previous custom positioning settings, if you have previously used position absolute or position fixed, please review your site.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.5.1 &#8211; 2019-03-04</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Inline Width (auto) not working (<a href="https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/7293" rel="nofollow ugc">#7293</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.5.0 &#8211; 2019-03-04</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Added Position Absolute &amp; Position Fixed for widgets (<a href="https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/5568" rel="nofollow ugc">#5568</a>)</li>\n<li>New: Added inline &amp; custom width options to place widgets side by side without columns (<a href="https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/4960" rel="nofollow ugc">#4960</a>)</li>\n<li>New: Added responsive options for Column (<a href="https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/2965" rel="nofollow ugc">#2965</a>, <a href="https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/7104" rel="nofollow ugc">#6898</a>, Props <a href="https://github.com/wayheming" rel="nofollow ugc">@wayheming</a>)</li>\n<li>New: Added Columns for Text Editor widget (<a href="https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/7104" rel="nofollow ugc">#7