				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Par <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/clubsereniamansion"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/975dfac27d0104a668ccffa7258cc96d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/975dfac27d0104a668ccffa7258cc96d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/clubsereniamansion" class="reviewer-name">Club Serenia Mansion <small>(clubsereniamansion)</small></a> le <span class="review-date">janvier 4, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">Thank you for free, it\'s best plugin for build website</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">For Wordpress, the best plugin ever</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="5 sur 5 étoiles" data-title-template="%s sur 5 étoiles" data-rating="5" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Par <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/dggabriel2020"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8a0c9be6d8984db39065cfc6904f3205?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8a0c9be6d8984db39065cfc6904f3205?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/dggabriel2020" class="reviewer-name">Gabriel <small>(dggabriel2020)</small></a> le <span class="review-date">janvier 2, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">Not much to say, prove it, test it, hate it then love it.</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">Robust but Complex and Difficult to Master</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="5 sur 5 étoiles" data-title-template="%s sur 5 étoiles" data-rating="5" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Par <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/clintongallagher"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/71a64c4263328322a1c51426939d15fe?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/71a64c4263328322a1c51426939d15fe?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/clintongallagher" class="reviewer-name">ClintonGallagher</a> le <span class="review-date">décembre 30, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">I am having a Joe Biden moment. I have written about CrocoBlock rather than --just-- Elementor...\n\nCrocoBlock has developed an extensive and comprehensive collection of widgets used with the Elementor Page Builder. However, the collection has several duplicate capabilities and most are quite complex and time consuming (difficult) to learn to master.\n\nThe company provides excellent support; direct-to-developer, videos and knowledge base articles however the complexity of what they have accomplished remains what it is. \n\nThere is a lot of old content from earlier releases that makes learning even more time consuming and difficult. Being a developer myself I --always-- date and version everything and share that publically. This is a Best Practice not adopted by CrocoBlock that would be in their best interest to adopt to solve the "old content" dilemma all vendors have to cope with as they move forward refining and changinge their product(s).\n\nBe prepared to allot "a lot" of time in your development budget for "a lot" of work learning what to do and more importantly what not to do until you have a few projects complete and are familiar with what features and functions work best for your use cases.\n\nCrocoBlock folks are Ukrainian and have an excellent command of English but here and there use nouns and other terms in ways that a native English speaker would not use so be prepared for a couple of "What the hell do they mean by that?" LOL\n\nWith all this said, CrocoBlock is proving themselves to be the best of the best in this domain and I highly recommend them above all other 3rd Parties that integrate with Elementor.</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">Very good!</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="4 sur 5 étoiles" data-title-template="%s sur 5 étoiles" data-rating="4" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Par <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/katayoondesign"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/71f809ecdcf7c486abe4ede3b1acfabb?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/71f809ecdcf7c486abe4ede3b1acfabb?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/katayoondesign" class="reviewer-name">katayoondesign</a> le <span class="review-date">décembre 30, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">I have been using your service for quite a while and I am very pleased with it! Thank you! \n\nThe only reason I\'m not giving five stars is that I assumed I would get better support with the premium version but it took too long to get a response. When you have this many users, you need to increase the number of people in your support team :) </div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">The best page builder</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="5 sur 5 étoiles" data-title-template="%s sur 5 étoiles" data-rating="5" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Par <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/dmpspcz"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/aacb96c8438321e345f13bcf3a76f00b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/aacb96c8438321e345f13bcf3a76f00b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/dmpspcz" class="reviewer-name">dmpspcz</a> le <span class="review-date">décembre 29, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">The best page builder\n</